Processes

INVENTORY
1. Create new box and sent to box queue
2. Review previous box stats
3. CRUD ramen, brands, box

ORDERS
1. Customer creates new order
2. Customer registers
3. Customer pays order
4. Create a new Stripe token
5. Create a new Stripe customer
6. Subscribe Stripe customer to subscription plan
7. If no errors, mark current month's order paid and customer subscribed
8. Order checks for address verification and shipping rate

SHIPPING
9. Order sent to shipping queue
10. Order marked shipped
11. Order complete

FINANCES
12. 30 days later customer charged
13. Reloop order process

CUSTOMERS
1. LTV
2. Churn-rate





1. Create fakers
from alfie.apps.fakers.models import *
Faker.objects.create_fakers()

2. Create profiles
Faker.objects.create_profile()

3. Create stripe plans
from alfie.apps.back.finance.stripeutil import *
create_plans()

4. Create ramen box

5. Create stripe tokens
Faker.objects.create_fake_tokens()

6. Create stripe customers
Faker.objects.create_fake_customers()

7. Create fake orders
Faker.objects.create_fake_orders()

8. Verify address
Faker.objects.verify_fake_addr()

9. Save last4 in orders
Order.objects.check_last4()

10. Check paid
Order.objects.check_paid()

11. Tally costs
Order.objects.check_stripe_fee()
Order.objects.set_shipping_cost()
Order.objects.tally_costs()

12. Pack orders
Order.objects.pack_all_boxes()

13. Ship orders
Order.objects.ship_all_boxes()

